        </caption>
        <graphic xlink:href="1471-2164-14-S1-S12-4"/>
      </fig>
      <p>The tool, including the source code and example data, is available from the Bielefeld University Bioinformatics Server: <ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="http://bibiserv.cebitec.uni-bielefeld.de/agglodel/">http://bibiserv.cebitec.uni-bielefeld.de/agglodel/</ext-link></p>
    </sec>
